    5. The Raid: Redeption  
    4. Terminator 2: Judgement Day  
    3. Enter the Dragon  
    2. Die Hard  
    1. Mad Max: Fury Road""")

    print("Which movie would you like to learn more about? Choose 10-1.")
    choice= input(">")
    if choice == '10':
        webbrowser.open_new("https://www.lionsgate.com/franchises/john-wick")
    if choice == '9':
        webbrowser.open_new(" ")

